comments: As a stationary player, Okoro (CLE) receives the pass and establishes his left foot as his pivot, which he lifts and re-plants as he starts his dribble.
Harris (BKN) firms up in his screening position in Nance Jr.'s (CLE) path and absorbs the contact.
Okoro (CLE) initiates contact across Harden's (BKN) right arm after his gather.
Green (BKN) and Nance Jr. (CLE) engage and disengage with one another as they move toward the elbow.
Harris (BKN) initiates contact with Nance Jr.'s (CLE) front that affects his FOM off ball.

Irving (BKN) and Sexton (CLE) engage with one another as the screen approaches and as they begin to disengage, Irving makes some contact with Sexton's face. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Harris (BKN) pins the ball against his side and resumes his dribble thereafter.
Osman (CLE) maintains legal guarding position as contact occurs with Harris (BKN) at the end of the drive.
Osman (CLE) brushes Harris' (BKN) right shoulder as he starts his upward shooting motion and marginal contact occurs.
Allen (CLE) and Green (BKN) engage and disengage with one another along the perimeter.
Nance Jr. (CLE) and Durant (BKN) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Irving's (BKN) right hand is extended forward and marginal contact occurs with Sexton's (CLE) left arm prior to Sexton losing control of the ball on his own.

Replay review of the foul called on Irving (BKN) pursuant to a coach's challenge is deemed successful.  Irving makes inadvertent contact with Sexton's (CLE) head during a legal move to the basket.  A jump ball is administered because the ball was loose at the time of the whistle.
Nance Jr. (CLE) makes marginal contact with Harden's (BKN) left arm as he secures the ball.
Nance Jr. (CLE) is moving alongside Harden's (BKN) path and absorbs the body contact made at the end of the drive.
Osman (CLE) engages and disengages with Irving (BKN) in the lane.
Harden (BKN) rests both hands against Nance Jr.'s (CLE) backside and marginal contact occurs prior to the hand-off.
Nance Jr. (CLE) and Harris (BKN) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Green (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Nance Jr.'s (CLE) path and does not deliver the contact.
Sexton (CLE) has his hand extended forward and marginal contact occurs with Irving's (BKN) front at the start of the drive.
Nance Jr. (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in Irving's (BKN) path and does not deliver the contact.
Irving (BKN) makes clean contact with the ball and causes it to become dislodged from Sexton (CLE), and Sexton legally re-gains control of the ball after it is dislodged.
Okoro (CLE) and Harris (BKN) engage and disengage with one another as the pick is set.
Harris (BKN) is moving alongside Osman's (CLE) path when marginal contact occurs with Osman's side during the driving shot attempt.
Osman (CLE) brings his off-arm towards Harris' (BKN) left arm and marginal contact occurs as Harris contests the driving shot attempt.
Okoro (CLE) initiates contact across Harden's (BKN) left arm after Harden picks up his dribble.
Durant (BKN) turns slightly as he firms up on his right foot and he absorbs the contact made with Sexton (CLE) as the screen is set.
Irving (BKN) and Sexton (CLE) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Harden (BKN) gathers the ball on his left foot and establishes his right foot as his pivot, which he lifts as he starts his dribble.
Osman (CLE) is turning away from Harden (BKN) and avoids making contact with Harden as he loses his balance.
Nance Jr. (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in Harris' (BKN) path following the hand-off and does not deliver the contact.
Harris (BKN) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Osman (CLE) and avoids making contact.
Harden (BKN) is moving toward Sexton (CLE) and marginal contact occurs with Sexton's feet as he is airborne during the rebound.
Nance Jr. (CLE) intentionally kicks the ball.
Nance Jr. (CLE) commits the take foul on Durant (BKN).
Harden (BKN) commits the take foul on Sexton (CLE).
Irving (BKN) legally contests Sexton's (CLE) jump shot attempt and marginal contact is initiated by Sexton extending his leg.
Nance Jr. (CLE) and Durant (BKN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Nance Jr. (CLE) legally contests Durant's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
